Check "Don't remind me again" option on the confirmation dialog that pops up on removal items on form editors.
Items are removed with warning message  and "Don't remind about removing" preference is checked

Precondition
EntityWithExtendsAndAttributesLiteralsMethodsContextWorkspace

1. Remove attribute
2. Check "Don't remind about removing" checkbox in warning message;
3. Open Tigerstripe/General Preferences
4. See that preference "Don't remind about removing" is checked
5. Remove attribute, method and constant with warning
